The paper discusses Ontology Learning, which is a subfield of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The focus is on mapping English language sentences into their equivalent Description Logic expressions, which involves Natural Language Processing (NLP) techniques and falls under Computational Linguistics (cs.CL). The use of DL expressions also involves Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Information Retrieval (cs.IR) techniques. Finally, the paper deals with building a knowledge base, which is related to Database Systems (cs.DB).
